                ->  Seq Scan on rental r  (cost=0.00..359.90 rows=27 width=0) (actual time=0.867..33.204 rows=278 loops=10)
                      Filter: (customer_id = c.customer_id)
                      Rows Removed by Filter: 160162
        SubPlan 2
          ->  Aggregate  (cost=70.91..70.92 rows=1 width=38) (actual time=2.244..2.244 rows=10 loops=10)
                ->  Bitmap Heap Scan on payment p  (cost=4.46..70.85 rows=27 width=6) (actual time=0.812..1.845 rows=278 loops=10)
                      Recheck Cond: (customer_id = c.customer_id)
